item.title: Murder of Sarah Stern
item.description: Join us on a gripping journey into the heart of a small coastal town as we delve deep into the chilling case of Sarah Stern's murder. In this true-crime podcast, we explore the enigmatic circumstances surrounding the 19-year-old's sudden disappearance, the relentless search for answers, and the shocking revelation that would leave a community in shock. Uncover the secrets, motives, and twists in this tragic tale of betrayal, deceit, and a relentless pursuit of justice... Feed: https://feeds.buzzsprout.com/1209845.rss
